---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Resume">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-12 tracking-tight">resume</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Asdrúbal Chirinos</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-8">
            Vision Architect | Bridging Business and Code for Success.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            With over 30 years of experience, I have dedicated my career to
            bridging the gap between business vision and technical execution. As
            a Solution Architect and Vision Facilitator, my mission is to help
            build bridges between visionaries and doers to turn bold ideas into
            reality.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-12 mb-6">Experience</h3>

        <div class="mb-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-2">
                <h4
                    class="font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
                >
                    PRODU
                </h4>
                <span class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">2018 – Present</span>
            </div>
            <p
                class="text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-3 font-medium"
            >
                IT/Developer Manager
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Serve as a Solution Architect, bridging business vision and
                technical execution. Gather strategic objectives from business
                leaders and translate them into clear development requirements.
                Provide inspirational leadership to the technology team as a
                player-coach, fostering creativity while ensuring alignment and
                successful delivery. Also optimized and secured the company's
                AWS cloud infrastructure.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-2">
                <h4
                    class="font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
                >
                    MANAGEMENT PLAZA
                </h4>
                <span class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">Jun 2015 – Jul 2018</span
                >
            </div>
            <p
                class="text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-3 font-medium"
            >
                Team Leader / Web Developer
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Led cross-functional product development by translating business
                requirements into actionable solutions. Recruited and
                coordinated teams across SharePoint, EDI, and Ionic platforms.
                Provided strategic oversight and mentorship, fostering
                collaboration and ensuring successful delivery.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-2">
                <h4
                    class="font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
                >
                    BIT LEVER
                </h4>
                <span class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">Jun 2015 – Jul 2018</span
                >
            </div>
            <p
                class="text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-3 font-medium"
            >
                Full Stack Developer
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Contributed to the early development of a contact center
                platform integrating gamification, business intelligence, and
                operational tools. Collaborated closely with the CEO and the
                development team to ensure the product met user needs and
                strategic goals.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-12 mb-6">Skills</h3>
        <ul
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 list-none pl-0 text-lg"
        >
            <li>Inspirational Leadership</li>
            <li>Effective Communication</li>
            <li>Solution Architecture</li>
            <li>Team Management</li>
            <li>Full-Stack Development</li>
            <li>WordPress, React, Node.js, AWS</li>
            <li>C#, .NET, PHP</li>
            <li>Using AI, under human supervision</li>
            <li>Strategic Planning</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-12 mb-6">Contact</h3>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            LinkedIn: <a
                href="https://linkedin.com/in/achirinos"
                target="_blank"
                class="font-medium hover:underline">linkedin.com/in/achirinos</a
            ><br />
            Location: Aguascalientes, Mexico
        </p>
    </div>
</Layout>
